        </div>
        <div class="check-item animate-in" style="animation-delay: 0.5s">
          <span class="check-mark">✓</span>
          <span>3 analysis sections on what matters this week</span>
        </div>
        <div class="check-item animate-in" style="animation-delay: 0.7s">
          <span class="check-mark">✓</span>
